Nice that they've fixed things so no one can take advantage of a server outage.<br>
<br>
HOWEVER, there's no mention of quicker character saves, or an option for a user to /save their character whenever they get xp or an item.<br>
<br>
As usual, SOE doesn't seem to care much about the downside of their server outages. Their only goal is to prevent people from taking advantage of the situation.<br>
<br>
75-95% of Players with lost items, buffs or xp? No big deal. They have to play more to get them back.<br>
<br>
1-2% of Players getting extra shots at an ubermob? Oooooh, we better work on this. Hire some more temps......<br>
<br>
<br>
Please note, I'm a little jaded in my view, I play on a server that crashes regularly. There's a rumor going around that the crashes are actually 'attacks' on the Stormhammer server. It will be interesting to see if the crashes stop now.....<br>
